quran[55]{c,v,t}:
  54,1,"Darngal ngal …ďadike, lewru ndun kadi seekike"
  54,2,"Si …ďe yi'ii maande, …ďe …óuurnoo …ďe wi'a: \"Ko mbilewu jokkondirngu"
  54,3,"∆Āe fenni, …ďe jokki mbelee…óe ma…ď…ďe. Hara le huunde kala no mari √Īii…ďirde"
  54,4,"Gom…óii kumpite arii e ma…ď…ďe, …óe ha…óitor…óum woni e mun"
  54,5,"[∆äum] ko √Īe√Ī∆īal yottiingal. Kono jertingol ngol nafaali"
  54,6,Selu …ďe. √Ďalnde noddoowo on noddoyta e huunde a√Īiniinde
  54,7,"jaasu…ďe ndaar…óe, hi…ďe yaltira e genaale …óen wano kanuuji caratoo…ói"
  54,8,"he√Īanii…ďe noddoowo on. Heefer…ďe …ďen wi'a: \"Ndee ko √Īalaande sattunde"
  54,9,"Ado ma…ď…ďe, yim…ďe nuuhu …ďen yedduno. ∆Āe fenni jeyaa…óo Amen on, …ďe wi'i : \"Ko jinnaa…óo!\", o kammbanaa"
  54,10,"O torii Joomi makko, wonnde : \"Min on ko mi foolaa…óo, faabo [lam]"
  54,11,"Men udditiri dammbu…óe kammu ngun, ndiyam wanncoojam"
  54,12,Men fuccitiri leydi ndin …ďulli. Ndiye …óen fottiri e yamiroore hoddiranoonde
  54,13,"Men roondori mo e [laana] lesaaka marka alluwe e peŇče"
  54,14,"hika dogira e ndenka Amen. ∆äum ko njo…ďdi [Nuuhu] fennanoo…óo on. @Corrected"
  54,15,"Gom…óii Men accirii [kon ko Men wa…ói …ďe] tasakuyee. Taw si woodi waajitoray…óo"
  54,16,Taskii ko honno lepte Am e jertinol (Am) wa'unoo
  54,17,Gom…óii Men newinirii Alqur'aanare nden waajitorgol. Hara wooday waajitor…óo
  54,18,Aadi'en fennuno. Taskee ko honno lepte Am e jertinol (Am) wa'unoo
  54,19,"Men wurtu e ma…ď…ďe henndu sattundu, e √Īalaande hiitaande, duumiinde"
  54,20,"hindu wippitira yim…ďe …ďen, wa si tawii ko …ďe da∆ī∆īe tamaro irtaa…óe"
  54,21,Taskee ko honno lepte Am …óen e jertinol (Am) ngol wa'unoo
  54,22,Gom…óii Men newinirii Alqur'aanare nden sabu waajitorgol. Hara wooday waajitor…óo
  54,23,Samuuda'en fennuno waaju ngun
  54,24,"…ďe wi'i: \"Kere ko ne…ó…óo gooto e amen woni ko men jokkata? Haray men wonii ontuma e nder majjere e tamperere"
  54,25,"Hara ko e makko jantoore nden werlaa hakkunde amen? Si ko woni, ko fenoowo nii, townitii…óo"
  54,26,"Aray …ďe annda (√Ďalnde) Janngo, ko hommbo woni fenoowo townitii…óo on"
  54,27,"Ko Men wurtiroo…ďe ngelooba ndewa mbam, jarribagol …ďe. Aynitu …ďe, mu√Ī√Īo…óaa"
  54,28,"Humpitu …ďe wonnde ndiyam …óam ko sennndaa…óam hakkunde ma…ď…ďe [e ngelooba mbam]; kala yaray ge…ďal mun"
  54,29,"∆Āe noddi wonndii…óo ma…ď…ďe, o jonni [kaafa kan], o sodi [mba]"
  54,30,Teskii ko honno lepte Am …óen e jertinol (Am) ngol wa'unoo
  54,31,"Ko haacaango wooturu tun Men wurti e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe wa'i wa ledde yooru…óe muncaa…óe"
  54,32,Gom…óii Men newinirii Alqur'aanare nden waajitorgol. Hara wooday waajitor…óo
  54,33,Yim…ďe Luutu …ďen fennuno jertine …óen
  54,34,"Men wurtuno henndu kaa∆īe e ma…ď…ďe, si wanaa e …ďeynguure Luutu nden, Men da…óndirno …ďen ka wenndo"
  54,35,"mo∆ī∆īere immorde e Amen. Ko non Men yo…ďitirta kala yettu…óo [neema Allah on]"
  54,36,Gom…óii le o jertinirno …ďe nanngal Amen cattungal ngal. Kono …ďe sikkitii jertinol ngol
  54,37,"Gom…óii …ďe …óa…ď…ďirno mo [bonidugol e ho…ó…ďe makko …ďen]. Men mehi gite ma…ď…ďe …óen. \"Mee…óee lepte …óen e jertinol Am ngol"
  54,38,"Gom…óii ko bimmbi law, woni ko lepte duumii…óe dawirani …ďe"
  54,39,Mee…óee lepte e jertinol Am
  54,40,Gom…óii Men newinirii Alqur'aanare nden waajitorgol. Hara wooday waajitor…óo
  54,41,Gom…óii jertinaango ngon arii e yim…ďe Fir'awna …ďen
  54,42,"∆Āe fenni Aayeeje Amen …óen fow. Men nanngiri …ďe, nanngal Foolu…óo Hattan…óo"
  54,43,Kere ko heefer…ďe mon …ďen …ďuri …ďeya mo∆ī∆īude? Kaa ko da…óugol woodani on ka ∆äeri
  54,44,"Kaa hara …ďe wi'ay : \"Menen ko men dental wallindiroo…ďe"
  54,45,"Aray nde dental [ma…ď…ďe] ngal foolee, …ďe runntina …ďabbe ma…ď…ďe"
  54,46,"Wurin ko Darngal ngal woni kammbaa ma…ď…ďe on, Ko Darngal non …ďuri mawnude e haa…óude"
  54,47,"Pellet, bom…ďe …ďen wonii e majjere e ooyunge"
  54,48,"√Ďalnde …ďe daasiroytee geece ma…ď…ďe …óen ka nder Yiite, (…ďe wi'anee): \"Mee…óee meemugol Saqara"
  54,49,Menen Men tagir huunde kala e e…ď…ďoore
  54,50,"Yamiroore Amen wonaali, si wanaa [konngol] gootol pet, [yaawira] wa hin∆īaango yiitere"
  54,51,Gom…óii Men halkiino yeradii…ďe mon. Hara wooday waajitoray…óo
  54,52,Kala huunde nde …ďe golli no ka nder …óeri
  54,53,"kala kadi toksum e mawnukum, ko winndaa…óum"
  54,54,"Pellet, gom…óu…ďe …ďen wonii e Aljannaaji e can…ói"
  54,55,"e toolorde goonga, ka Laam…óo Hattan…óo"